INSERT INTO `tb_blog` VALUES ('9', '初入职场，如何快速成为一名合格的初级工程师。', 'admin', '年后3月份，迎来了各大企业招聘实习生的高峰，接着就是校招了。从3月到9月，这半年间会有大量的毕业生进入企业，开始他们的职业生涯。', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #e2ecf6; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; margin: 0px !important 0px 16px 0px;\" data-spm-anchor-id=\"a2c4e.11154000.rtdmain.i1.56a8a411zqWdo9\">年后3月份，迎来了各大企业招聘实习生的高峰，接着就是校招了。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #e2ecf6; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" data-spm-anchor-id=\"a2c4e.11154000.rtdmain.i2.56a8a411zqWdo9\">从3月到9月，这半年间会有大量的毕业生进入企业，开始他们的职业生涯。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #e2ecf6; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" data-spm-anchor-id=\"a2c4e.11154000.rtdmain.i3.56a8a411zqWdo9\">技术岗位的同学一般都会从初级工程师一路向中级、高级进发，最终成为技术专家。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #e2ecf6; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">初级工程师作为技术岗位的起始，承担着从学生到工程师的转变，尤为重要。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #e2ecf6; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">对于初入职的同学来说，要尽快确定自己的发展方向，度过这个时期。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #e2ecf6; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">对于公司来讲，初入职的同学要尽快的达到可以工作的要求。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #e2ecf6; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">那么对于下边的这三个问题，大家是怎么看待的。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #e2ecf6; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">问题1：你如何定义初级工程师，你认为的初、中、高级工程师都是什么样的</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #e2ecf6; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">问题2：初级工程师应该具备什么样的技能和品质</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; color: #24292e; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; 